    "Name": "Hermes II HER-2M",
    "Details": "Also known as the 'Mercury', this variant of the Hermes II was introduced in 2802 and used primarily by SAFE's Dark Shadows units. A larger VOX 280 engine was installed to bring the 'Mech's top speed up to 118.8 km/h, although this necessitated the removal of the AC/5, eliminating the 'Mech's long-range firepower. To make up for this, short-range firepower was increased with two additional medium lasers and two machine guns mounted in the right torso. Half a ton of machine gun ammo was stored in the left torso while an additional single heat sink was added.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Easy to Maintain</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.02</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limit: Left Lower</color>",
